Class HeldLockAnalyzer

java.lang.Object
com.google.errorprone.bugpatterns.threadsafety.HeldLockAnalyzer
public class HeldLockAnalyzer
extends Object
A method body analyzer. Responsible for tracking the set of held locks, and checking accesses to guarded members.
Author:
cushon@google.com (Liam Miller-Cushon)
